text: Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwantesile wanganyammwe kuwa wawinjila pachilambo (panyuma pakwajonanga wakala), ni wanyakwile pa uchimbichimbi wane mwajenumanja pachanya pa wane kuti an'dije mayeso pa ichindu yampele, chisimu Ambuje wenu ni wachitema pakupeleka ipotesi, nambo soni Walakweo ni Wakululuka kusyene, Wachanasa channope
